# MOBILE::CELL_SET_INPUT

## Summary
Lets code know what the player's latest input was (ie up/down/left/right/select) to trigger appropriate thumb anims

## Parameters
* **CELL_INPUT** cellInput

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
For move the finger of player, the value of int goes 1 at 5.
